Feature: Data Scoping    Scenario: User only sees their own data     Given I am logged in     And another user exists with data     When I visit my dashboard     Then I should see my data     And I should not see the other user's data    Scenario: User cannot access another user's data     Given I am logged in     And another user exists with data     When I attempt to view the other user's data     Then I should see an unauthorized error message    Scenario: Admin can view all user data       Given I am logged in as an admin     And multiple users exist with data     When I visit the admin dashboard     Then I should see all user data